msgstr ""
"Seo an cód don imreoir ag baint úsáide as comharthaí chun an piléar a astú:"

msgid ""
"In the main scene, we then connect the player's signal (it will appear in "
"the \"Node\" tab of the Inspector)"
msgstr ""
"Sa phríomhradharc, nascaímid comhartha an imreora ansin (beidh sé le "
"feiceáil i gcluaisín “Nód” an Cigire)"

msgid ""
